<epp:phrase id="hefce_oa:test_title:COMPLIANT"><epc:phrase ref="hefce"/> Open Access compliance</epp:phrase>
<epp:phrase id="hefce_oa:test_description:COMPLIANT">To be compliant, an item must meet at least one of the following conditions:
<ul>
	<li>The <strong>deposit</strong>, <strong>discovery</strong> and <strong>access</strong> requirements are met.</li>
	<li>There is a <strong>deposit exception</strong>.</li>
	<li>There is an <strong>access exception</strong> and the <strong>deposit</strong> and <strong>discovery</strong> requirements are met.</li>
	<li>There is a <strong>technical exception</strong>.</li>
	<li>There is an <strong>'other' exception</strong>.</li>
</ul>
</epp:phrase>

<epp:phrase id="hefce_oa:test_title:DEP">Deposit</epp:phrase>
<epp:phrase id="hefce_oa:test_description:DEP">To be deposit compliant, all of the following conditions must be met.</epp:phrase>
<epp:phrase id="hefce_oa:test_title:DEP_COMPLIANT">The output must have been deposited as the authorâ€™s accepted and final peer reviewed text.</epp:phrase>
<epp:phrase id="hefce_oa:test_description:DEP_COMPLIANT">
<blockquote><epc:phrase ref="hefce_oa:test_description:DEP_COMPLIANT:policy"/></blockquote>
<p><em><epc:phrase ref="hefce_oa:test_description:DEP_COMPLIANT:eprints"/></em></p>
</epp:phrase>
<epp:phrase id="hefce_oa:test_description:DEP_COMPLIANT:policy"><epc:phrase ref="hefce_oa:policy:para:20"/></epp:phrase>
<epp:phrase id="hefce_oa:test_description:DEP_COMPLIANT:eprints">The <strong><epc:phrase ref="eprint_fieldname_hoa_date_fcd"/></strong> must be set (ie. the item is a compliant deposit).</epp:phrase>

<epp:phrase id="hefce_oa:test_title:DEP_TIMING">The output must have been deposited as soon after the point of acceptance as possible.</epp:phrase>
<epp:phrase id="hefce_oa:test_description:DEP_TIMING">
<blockquote><epc:phrase ref="hefce_oa:test_description:DEP_TIMING:policy"/></blockquote>
<p><em><epc:phrase ref="hefce_oa:test_description:DEP_TIMING:eprints"/></em></p>
</epp:phrase>
<epp:phrase id="hefce_oa:test_description:DEP_TIMING:policy">
<epc:phrase ref="hefce_oa:policy:para:18"/>
<br/>
<epc:phrase ref="hefce_oa:policy:para:19"/>
</epp:phrase>
<epp:phrase id="hefce_oa:test_description:DEP_TIMING:eprints">
The <strong><epc:phrase ref="eprint_fieldname_hoa_date_fcd"/></strong> must be no later than three months after the <strong><epc:phrase ref="eprint_fieldname_hoa_date_acc"/></strong>. If the <strong><epc:phrase ref="eprint_fieldname_hoa_date_acc"/></strong> is before 1st April 2018, <strong><epc:phrase ref="eprint_fieldname_hoa_date_fcd"/></strong> must be no later than three months after the <strong><epc:phrase ref="eprint_fieldname_hoa_date_pub"/></strong>.
</epp:phrase>

<epp:phrase id="hefce_oa:test_title:DIS">Discovery</epp:phrase>
<epp:phrase id="hefce_oa:test_description:DIS">To be discovery compliant, all of the following conditions must be met:</epp:phrase>

<epp:phrase id="hefce_oa:test_title:DIS_DISCOVERABLE">The output must be presented in a way that allows it to be discovered by readers.</epp:phrase>
<epp:phrase id="hefce_oa:test_description:DIS_DISCOVERABLE">
<blockquote><epc:phrase ref="hefce_oa:test_description:DIS_DISCOVERABLE:policy"/></blockquote>
<p><em><epc:phrase ref="hefce_oa:test_description:DIS_DISCOVERABLE:eprints"/></em></p>
</epp:phrase>
<epp:phrase id="hefce_oa:test_description:DIS_DISCOVERABLE:policy">
<epc:phrase ref="hefce_oa:policy:para:23"/>
<br/>
<epc:phrase ref="hefce_oa:policy:para:24"/>
<br/>
<epc:phrase ref="hefce_oa:policy:para:25"/>
</epp:phrase>
<epp:phrase id="hefce_oa:test_description:DIS_DISCOVERABLE:eprints">
The item must be in the <epc:phrase ref="eprint_fieldopt_eprint_status_archive"/>.
</epp:phrase>

<epp:phrase id="hefce_oa:test_title:ACC">Access</epp:phrase>
<epp:phrase id="hefce_oa:test_description:ACC">To be access compliant, all of the following conditions must be met.</epp:phrase>

<epp:phrase id="hefce_oa:test_title:ACC_TIMING">The output must meet the access requirements as soon as possible.</epp:phrase>
<epp:phrase id="hefce_oa:test_description:ACC_TIMING">
<blockquote><epc:phrase ref="hefce_oa:test_description:ACC_TIMING:policy"/></blockquote>
<p><em><epc:phrase ref="hefce_oa:test_description:ACC_TIMING:eprints"/></em></p>
</epp:phrase>
<epp:phrase id="hefce_oa:test_description:ACC_TIMING:policy">
<epc:phrase ref="hefce_oa:policy:para:30"/>
<br/>
<epc:phrase ref="hefce_oa:policy:para:31"/>
</epp:phrase>
<epp:phrase id="hefce_oa:test_description:ACC_TIMING:eprints">
If no embargo applies, the <strong><epc:phrase ref="eprint_fieldname_hoa_date_foa"/></strong> must be less than one month after the <strong><epc:phrase ref="eprint_fieldname_hoa_date_fcd"/></strong>. Otherwise, the <strong><epc:phrase ref="eprint_fieldname_hoa_date_foa"/></strong> must be less than one month after the embargo expiry date (<strong><epc:phrase ref="eprint_fieldname_hoa_date_pub"/></strong> + <strong><epc:phrase ref="eprint_fieldname_hoa_emb_len"/>)</strong>.
</epp:phrase>

<epp:phrase id="hefce_oa:test_title:ACC_EMBARGO">Embargo periods should not exceed the following maxima</epp:phrase>
<epp:phrase id="hefce_oa:test_description:ACC_EMBARGO">
<blockquote><epc:phrase ref="hefce_oa:test_description:ACC_EMBARGO:policy"/></blockquote>
<p><em><epc:phrase ref="hefce_oa:test_description:ACC_EMBARGO:eprints"/></em></p>
</epp:phrase>
<epp:phrase id="hefce_oa:test_description:ACC_EMBARGO:policy">
<epc:phrase ref="hefce_oa:policy:para:32"/>
</epp:phrase>
<epp:phrase id="hefce_oa:test_description:ACC_EMBARGO:eprints">
The <strong><epc:phrase ref="eprint_fieldname_hoa_emb_len"/></strong> must not exceed the stated maxima for the target <strong><epc:phrase ref="eprint_fieldname_hoa_ref_pan"/></strong>.
</epp:phrase>

